Title: Kent Spiral Radial Pure Bristle Dressing & Styling
Description: Kent is a 230-Year-Old brand of premium brushes from the United Kingdom. Known for its legacy of producing the largest, widest, most premium and highest quality brushes, the company has a range spanning head to toe. Kent Super Premium series is the one of the finest ranges of Kent for the discerning few. All brushes in the super premium range are hand crafted, hand-finished and made with the choicest materials sourced from the best possible suppliers around the world. The hallmark of this series is the use of real bristle instead of conventional cheap plastic. Brushing hair is the simplest beauty treatment there is, easing tension and stress from the head and neck. Brushing with real bristle stimulates and encourages essential oils in the scalp to flow through the hair strands nourishing and protecting each hair strand, leaving it smooth and naturally shiny. Bristle strengths vary for fine or thick hair, and for best brushing performance it is important to use the right bristle strength. A bristle is similar to a hair in construction, and sections cut from nearer the root of the bristle are strongest and best for brushing thick hair, while sections from the tip or flag end are softer and more suited to fine hair and a delicate scalp. All brush designs in the Kent premium range are suitable for traditional brushing or blow drying. No effort has been spared. No corners have been cut in the craftsmanship and material used in the Kent Super premium series. This range is for the discerning few who prefer nothing but the very best in LIFE. Always!

The notes are young, watery, icy, dewy and airy.Herbal Roots Sea Breeze a delicate and unique aroma with water lavender notes accords for a breeze of fragrance straight from the Pacific. The opening is fruity, and the fragrance settles into a lavender dry down.It is light and distinguished; the perfect harmony between sweetness and saltiness.The fragrance is extremely refreshing and addictive that instantly makes you feel enjoying in any vacation.Spray it on after a shower or anytime when you need to feel a lift of spirits.This mist will keep you feeling renewed and will help moisturize your skin.Use it on your pillows for some bedtime aromatherapy, spritz some on your clean laundry as a dryer sheet alternative.
